text: Elati (, meaning "pine tree") is a mountain on the Greek island of Lefkada. It is the island's highest peak. ==Settlements== Settlements at or near the mountain are: *Agios Petros, southwest *Karya, northwest ==See also== *List of mountains in Greece ==References== Category:Mountains of Greece Category:Lefkada Category:Landforms of Lefkada (regional unit) Category:Mountains of the Ionian Islands (region)
title: Elati (mountain)
